John C. Glenn, Public Administrator of Queens County, as Administrator of the Estate of Thekla Haink, Deceased, Respondent, v. Edward H. Bousfield, Appellant.

Motion for leave to appeal to the Court of Appeals denied. Present — MacCrate, Acting P. J., Schmidt, Beldock, Murphy and Ughetta, JJ. [See ante, p. 894.]
